      },
      "lineNbr": 44,
      "author": {
        "id": 5015
      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-09-12T13:57:15Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yeah, that\u0027s the idea.  The Job is IN_PROGRESS from the moment it\u0027s triggered (RUNNING is meaningless because the Job consists of a set of Tasks which may be untriggered, pending, running, finished, failed, etc) until all of its Tasks have finished or failed.",
      "parentUuid": "8bc2da6f_daf725ec",
      "revId": "4e6dc9e968cb3a79aba33b7db73b0a8fa5366628",
